- Read mobius:atlas:paw:liveness via kvGetRaw (matches PAW heartbeat write)
- TripwireSparkline PAW LIVE/DARK indicator
- ignore-build: kaizencycle always builds; cursoragent bot gate; [deploy] escape
- Document redeploy/promote bypass in docs/DEPLOY.md
